query:
SELECT 
  s.id,
  s.name,
  s.symbol,
  COUNT(t.id) as trade_count,
  DATE_FORMAT(MIN(t.exitDate), '%Y-%m-%d') as earliest_trade,
  DATE_FORMAT(MAX(t.exitDate), '%Y-%m-%d') as latest_trade
FROM strategies s
LEFT JOIN trades t ON s.id = t.strategyId
GROUP BY s.id, s.name, s.symbol
ORDER BY s.id;
